Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:12.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よみがえった王は 自らをメルエムと名乗り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:12.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They are definitely coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:24.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何が起こってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:24.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, an item sold for ten thousand can be turned around for a \Nhundred million the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:28.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}総帥様は　どこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:28.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can make a fortune instantly. It's where dreams come true. Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれは敵の能力。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyway, do you think Kurapika \Nand Leorio will show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:45.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵本体にダメージを与えなければ 恐らく消えませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:45.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They promised to meet us here. I'm sure they'll come. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:49.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ほう　面白い。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:49.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They might try to contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}試すか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey, you have to buy a phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's standard Hunter gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:57.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさに　あれは俺の…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:57.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ah, that's true. Hey! Welcome! This one's great...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おぉ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That model is for people \Nwho only make calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}う…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Leorio! Yo! I would recommend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's a little heavy and pricey, but it includes a translator for the \Ntwo hundred languages used worldwide. What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我の能力　我のためにあらず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:33.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Go with this one. I'll buy one, too! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:37.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王にお渡しするための ものだったのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:37.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Two, please. Two will cost four hundred thousand. Four hundred thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー。 はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's expensive, pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理屈に合わぬな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Thanks, Leorio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ… あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But, damn, 110,580 Jenny apiece, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:51.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}攻撃した相手に憑く能力を 知っていたということは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:51.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's a new model, so that's a \Nfair price in this market. Still, talk about overkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:58.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}間近で　それを実際に見たか お主自身が その能力を受けたかのいずれか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:58.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've never seen a cell phone purchase greeted \Nwith applause before. But you really saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どちらだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just so you know, that was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私が攻撃を受けました。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's the last person you \Nwould find at an auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:19.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今現在　お主に あれは憑いていない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:19.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So how are you guys doing? What do you mean? You've trained and gotten stronger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なのに　なぜ敵は生きている？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:30.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お主は　どうやって 敵の能力を解除したのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:30.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You returned the tag to \NHisoka at Heavens Arena? And you have to be pretty good \Nto make it to the 200s...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}答えよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How strong have you gotten now? Hey, did you learn Nen, Leorio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}条件を交わしました。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:39.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, you bet. Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:46.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの能力を 解除すれば　仲間を助けると。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:46.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really? Why would I lie to you? It's the ability to build up a shroud \Nof aura, one's own life force...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:54.00,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間もろとも 始末することはできたはず。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:54.00,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's Ten, one of the four major \Nprinciples for learning Nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜ　しなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Eh? There's more to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:08.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　敵の何かに 負けたくなかったのだと。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:08.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Greed Island ? What's that? A legendary game. We're trying to get a copy at the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.45,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}たとえ敵とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.45,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But why a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:16.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その場で約束を破棄にすることは 敗北に感じたのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:16.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I think this game holds a \Nclue to finding my dad. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ばかな！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The game holds a clue to finding your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:21.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そんな あやふやな個人的感情が理由で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:21.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What do you mean? Well, it's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王に牙むく者どもを　むざむざ 見過ごしたというのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Anyway, the problem is the cost. How much are we talking? The lowest starting bid is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}返す言葉はございませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}8.9 billion?! How much do you have? We made some bad investments, so we're down to 5 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余は偽るなと命じただけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Listen up, kids... This event is held at Southern Piece, \Nthe world's finest auction house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:49.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それに対し　真実で応えた者に とがの　あろうはずもない。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:49.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The money you have won't \Ncover the entry fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But the game has a low difficulty rank\Non the Hunter site's treasure list.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:56.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}プフ！ はっ！ ユピー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:56.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Really? Because you only need \Nmoney to get a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It always comes back to money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お互い　不便な体になったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This world runs on money! Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:13.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我らは　肉体も心も つながってしまった。 ３名の間で もはや　隠し事は　かなわぬぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:13.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That just means that a real \Ntreasure can't be bought. If you can't obtain an item \Nlike this with ease, you can't be considered \Na pro Hunter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But first, we need money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:22.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王。 行くぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:22.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll need some starting funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's find a way to make \Nsome money in Yorknew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その　後ろめたさの感情に 感づいての
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Damn! What's wrong?! I created a complete \Nduplicate of the program.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最後の忠告でしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why aren't any events being triggered?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:47.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでも！ たとえ死罪になろうとも！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:47.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Did Kil somehow trick me? No... No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王のため！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He isn't capable of creating a fake game, and he's not stupid enough \Nto lie over a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.46,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生物統一のため！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.46,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to know the answer. I'll do whatever it takes to \Nuncover this secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:08.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれは　いらぬ！ それが王のため
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:08.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have 12.7 billion left. I'll need at least twice that amount
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}違う　こっちだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to guarantee a winning bid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}へい！ あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Dad, I want to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:20.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ばらけてちゃ 俺にダメージ与えられねえぜ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:20.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll kill fifteen people, \Nso lend me 15 billion. Got it. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Autopilot engaged to Lingon Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:30.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}シカトか！　待て　こら！ 俺とやんなきゃ ポットクリンは取れねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:30.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I think I was ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:34.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー！ 突然　敵が目の前に現れました！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:34.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The last time I went outside. Huh? Swap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.43,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれを憑けた奴は 瞬間移動もできるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.43,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.97,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}別の奴だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.97,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}"Swap."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分と　その周囲を 透明にできる奴がいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}An auction technique. Slang for the exchange of goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}カメレオンみたいな奴だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Also see "Bind." What's a bind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:51.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}名前は知らねえが　師団長の１人 つまり裏切り者だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:51.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}"Bind." The seller names a condition \Nbesides money as their price.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:56.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人間はおろか 裏切り者まで見逃した ということですか？　あなたは！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:56.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The winning bid will be the \None that comes closest to meeting that condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:08:00.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ…　どんな罰でも受ける。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:08:00.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Condition? No idea what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王！　この件は　奴らを倒し次第…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}構わぬ　不問だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's another kind of auctioning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:14.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これはむしろ　我々キメラが 進化する過程において 乗り越えねばならぬ試練とみた。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:14.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tonight, at 9 PM, the mummy of Princess Corco \Nwill be auctioned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:23.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ユピー　お主の精神的揺らぎも 裏切り者の心変りも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:23.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ivlenkov, Tocino, and Baise, you'll handle the bidding. Will three people be enough? Each group of bidders \Nis limited to three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:28.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}受け入れた上で　次へ進む。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:28.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You cannot bring weapons, \Nrecorders, or communication devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:36.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人は我々が　さらなる次元へ 上るための　いけにえ。 最高のな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:36.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All on-site security is handled by \Nthe Mafia that runs the auction, so there's rarely any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}我らに残る　人の我の残滓など
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to turn every Mafia member, \Nworldwide, against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:47.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}さまつな不確定要素にすぎぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:47.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This auction is built on trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:54.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王の意見が爆発の前後で １８０度　違うのも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:54.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which is why the Mafia don't \Nuse security cameras. The unspoken rule is that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}衝撃によるものか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:57.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}any grudges and the like are left outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:01.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}否！　どちらも王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:01.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which means that if anything does happen, their testimony will decide everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:07.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵の能力が 透明ならば　触れれば分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:07.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Their words are treated as gospel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:12.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分身として ものが見える 限界まで細かく分散し
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:12.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So it's imperative to make \Na good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}探索範囲を拡大！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't start any petty fights. Avoid talking to anyone \Noutside this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:25.01,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}野郎　完全に標的は 俺じゃ　ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:25.01,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What about the rest of us? Basho and Linssen will cover the rear entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:29.51,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}急に引き返して来て 一体　誰を狙ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:29.51,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Kurapika and Melody will \Ntake the front entrance. Squala and I will guard the lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:36.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やはり 裏切り者のメレオロンか？ なら　絶対ヤバい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:36.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And with that, the mission begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}絶対に　メレオロンを死守する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come on down! Let's have some \Nconditional auctioning fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:56.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}細かく分裂したら　プフの分身は 見えなくなってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:56.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A diamond worth three million. Comes with the appraisal of the \Nstore where I just bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本体と違って　分身のほうは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Arm wrestling will decide the winning bid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}実物大でないと 捉えられないのだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The first person to beat this \Nboy wins the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:10.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}突然　現れたリーゼントは 明らかに　おとり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:10.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, let's start the auction! Yeah! It's mine! I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私達が　カメレオンを 裏切り者と認識したことは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Count me in! Okay, don't push... Form a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:20.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あちらも承知でしょう つまり　私が 裏切り者を処分するため
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:20.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Adjust your strength to \Nmatch the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:23.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}戻って来たと奴らは考える
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:23.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Every now and then, \Npretend to be struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仮に現在　カメレオンが 周りの者を透明にしながら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, you're first! You need to pay the entry fee up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:32.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逃亡　潜伏しており その中に　あの娘がいるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:32.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here you go... 10,000 Jenny. Thank you, step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:37.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}追い詰められれば カメレオンをかばい 娘を置いて行くはず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:37.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, clasp hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:43.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜならば　私が狙っているのは カメレオンだと思っているから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:43.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just follow my instructions. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ピトーが 必死に治療していた娘を
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You get a single round! Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:50.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私が殺しに戻るなど 想像すらできないはず
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:50.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:56.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}より好都合！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:56.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あちらから　条件付きで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:02.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}娘を　私に差し出すことすら 期待できます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:02.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You almost have it... Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確かめてみようぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, so close! Damn, I lost to a little kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:33.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.91,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}地下倉庫への扉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.91,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But to reach 8.9 billion, we're going to need 889,999 wins. Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:50.50,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど　私に透明能力が バレていることも承知の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:50.50,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And you lose! Next, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}二者択一ということですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:04.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私の分身を　さらに分散し 弱体化させようという作戦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:04.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's gotta be running out of steam. He looks tired, \Nand he's sweating hard. Don't lose before I get my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:10.49,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いや　あっち あっち　あっち！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:10.49,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I feel bad about tricking everyone. I'm even breaking out in a cold sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:11.99,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.49,0:12:11.99,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}at the idea of making so \Nmuch money so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}二択は二択
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Let's have a fair contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:37.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だが　裏切り者か娘かの二択？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:37.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.94,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私のターゲットが　どちらなのか 判断するのが狙いか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.94,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Ready... Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:19.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}目的は　こっちか！ 娘を殺し　しばらく王の目に 触れぬ所に隠すだけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:19.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, too bad! You lose! Good job, girl! Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分身でもできる！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.93,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１２分で！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.93,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こいつ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:38.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well? I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とんでもなく…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He's strong. That little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:45.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}速い こっちが本命か？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:45.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I sort of wanted that diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:48.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鬼ごっこなら付き合うぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:48.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You should've used your left hand. Yes, why didn't you use \Nyour stronger hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ひと晩中でもな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:56.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…　あの反応の速さ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:56.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He extended his right hand, \Nso I did the same. I'd like to challenge him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:14:01.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全力の私でも 捕らえることは困難か…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:14:01.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can't. No time. We have our job. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}早くしないと王が着く！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Besides, buying and \Nbidding would be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうする？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:05.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:10.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}窮地の中　思い立つ　悪魔の策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:10.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If we want something, we take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あった！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No way! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最高の魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can you hear me? \NI'm ready to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.44,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵の手に渡すわけには いかない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.44,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes, her tantrum—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうだわ　追ってる人の声は
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That is, her crying exhausted her, \Nand she's asleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:49.48,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}総帥様のおそばにいた人のもの ならば　王とは総帥様のこと じゃあ　この人は… この人の仲間は一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:49.48,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't know what will \Nhappen when she wakes. I vow to obtain the items she desires, but her goal is to participate \Nin the bidding personally. So she'll be disappointed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:54.98,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなた方のゆがんだ正義感は 決して人民のためにならない！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:54.98,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}when she wakes up and realizes \Nthat she missed her chance. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まずは　娘に魔法をかける
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:59.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll adjust my schedule and \Nhead over personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:04.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}猜疑心を呼び起こす 魔法の言葉 王も我々も
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:04.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}For now, just be sure to get \Nthat mummy princess, so we can get Neon in a good mood again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:07.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}対話による歩み寄りを 望んでいます！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:07.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:15.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今すぐ彼女を解放しなさい！ 野郎　好き勝手ほざきやがって 何　考えてんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:15.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's me. How's it going? Nothing unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}離すて。 え？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No changes visible from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ワダすを降ろすてください！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなた変です！ 痛っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We'll notify you if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何かビリビリするす！ ちょっ…　えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Still, they're being quite thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何言ってんだ　ばか！ 俺は　あんたを助けに来たんだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Only Mafia security are allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウソです！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}within five hundred meters \Nof the auction house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:38.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ウソって…　お前　俺より あの虫　信じんのかよ？ 虫？　何言ってんですか あなたこそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:38.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If they didn't do that, the surroundings \Nwould be crawling with thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:42.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}くっ…　そうだ こいつ　目が見えねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:42.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're practically announcing that \Nunwholesome practices are going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}説明できねえかも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will the Phantom Troupe
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ　惜しい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}really show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:57.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クッフフ… いとも簡単に毒は回った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:57.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:02.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}背負った娘が抵抗すれば あなたの素早さも半減
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:02.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's the same sound I heard earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:10.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どういうことだ？ 今　確かに俺じゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:10.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You see, I happened to see you \Nleaving the Hunter agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:15.41,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺すつもりで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:15.41,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When you walked past me, your heart was playing a melody of rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:21.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逃げられて　よし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:21.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}May I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}抵抗してガキが　ひるんだ隙に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}娘を殺せば　なお　よし
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Scarlet eyes. Exactly what...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:32.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}コムギさん！　賊にとって あなたは大事な人質！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:32.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}do they mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:35.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}決して 殺されることはありません！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:35.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もっと動いて！　もっと暴れて！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:39.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No real reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}すぐ助けます！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Curiosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When you saw the image \Non the data card, your heartbeat was even more fearsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:55.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}寝かしたから無理。 まっ　そっちの事情は 知んねえけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:55.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It played a melody of boundless fury.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:59.95,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}てめぇが　ムカつくってことは 十分　分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:59.95,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I suppose that I can't lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:12.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この「円」の中に入ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:12.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Our eyes are normally brown, but they're red when we're excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.90,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}殺す。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:13.90,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So I wear black contacts \Nto avoid discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}タァ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I am searching for the eyes taken from my brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:32.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分身つってもさ 元は全部　お前の細胞だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:32.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will you report this to Dalzollene?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}焼け焦げれば　そこは死ぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:35.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I will not. I do not wish to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}電撃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You could read my intention? A heartbeat is always honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:47.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}来いよ… そぎ取って　はぜてやるから。 くっ…。 苦戦しているのか？ あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:47.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When you began to confess \Nyour true nature to me, your heartbeat was calm, but frigid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:53.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}焦燥が伝わって来るが。 手を貸すぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:53.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The heartbeat of one who is prepared to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:19:01.42,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ご心配には及びません。 メルエム様は　何よりも ご記憶の回復が最優先。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:19:01.42,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your heart said that, though you would hold \Nno grudges, I was fair game if I talked. Why did you take this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:05.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}賊ごとき 本体が戻れば問題ありません。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:05.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Why do you ask? I'll probably lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:12.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それよりも ご覧ください　メルエム様！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:12.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll know if you're lying by your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}思い出されましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm also a pro Hunter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.37,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全ては王のため！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:20.37,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A Music Hunter, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:26.38,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全てが王のもの！ これが余の…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:26.38,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm looking for a certain musical score.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:33.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}これら 知恵回らぬ下層愚民を統べ 生物山脈の頂に立つことこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:33.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You aren't lying, but you are concealing \Nsomething important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:40.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}王　本来の光あふれる宿命！ 天務にございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:40.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, let's just say that you're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何かが違う。 はっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A solo said to have been \Ncomposed by the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余は…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are four versions... \NFor the piano, violin, flute, and harp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:04.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まだ　他に何か これではない何かを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:04.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If a human plays or listens to the piece, it's said that disaster will befall them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.92,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.92,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Isn't that just a myth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:12.47,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}生物大統一より 大切な目標などあろうはずが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:12.47,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I doubt something like that \Ncould exist in reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}痛みが引かぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:27.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've heard the flute version.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.88,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}敵との攻防で…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.88,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My friend who played the piece died, \Ntheir entire body like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:40.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}メルエム様が 宮殿を出た後のことです。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:40.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That friend learned a single \Nmovement from someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:44.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}余が　いつもいた場所は　どこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:44.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}who said never to play the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:49.39,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今は崩れて　跡形もなく。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:49.39,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That day, we were drunk and giddy. My body was destroyed, but I \Ngained this ability in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:58.87,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}残った所を見てみるか。 はっ！　何か記憶の 手掛かりになるようなものが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:58.87,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}However, I wish to restore my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}見つかるかもしれませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm willing to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't want anyone else \Nto end up like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:07.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うぅ…　まずい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:07.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So I'll find the score and destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:11.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なり得る…　軍儀の盤や駒が…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:11.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I chose this job because
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:17.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}記憶を呼び起こす鍵に！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:17.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}it will be more efficient to \Nwork from the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:20.89,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}回収処分せねば　全て！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:20.89,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.40,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あそこだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.40,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How will Kurapika, now a \NNostrade Family bodyguard, deal with them?
